		<h3>Backbone.js</h3>
		
		<p>Understand the importance of snappy, interactive web applications? 
We do too; that's why we use Backbone.js to build highly interactive 
client-side (translate: FAST) applications for our clients. </p>

		<p>Backbone.js is a super sleek JavaScript client-side framework that 
allows the browser to very quickly and efficiently respond to changes in
 data by utilizing the observer pattern on its models. This means that 
most of the changes happening within your application are 
instantaneously reflected in the browser, making your app snappier than 
ever.  </p>

		<p>Sometimes speed counts. When it does, businesses want the 
advantages of emerging solutions like Backbone.js. We're employing this 
technology for our clients and our products, creating rocket-fueled web 
applications where it matters most. </p>
